{"thi-ap7:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap7:0.2":"Sumedhavagga ","thi-ap7:0.3":"7 Katacchubhikkhadayikatheriapadana ","thi-ap7:1.1":"“Pindacaram carantassa, ","thi-ap7:1.2":"tissanamassa satthuno; ","thi-ap7:1.3":"Katacchubhikkham paggayha, ","thi-ap7:1.4":"buddhasetthassa dasaham. ","thi-ap7:2.1":"Patiggahetva sambuddho, ","thi-ap7:2.2":"tisso lokagganayako; ","thi-ap7:2.3":"Vithiya santhito sattha, ","thi-ap7:2.4":"aka me anumodanam. ","thi-ap7:3.1":"‘Katacchubhikkham datvana, ","thi-ap7:3.2":"tavatimsam gamissasi; ","thi-ap7:3.3":"Chattimsadevarajunam, ","thi-ap7:3.4":"mahesittam karissasi. ","thi-ap7:4.1":"Pannasam cakkavattinam, ","thi-ap7:4.2":"mahesittam karissasi; ","thi-ap7:4.3":"Manasa patthitam sabbam, ","thi-ap7:4.4":"patilacchasi sabbada. ","thi-ap7:5.1":"Sampattim anubhotvana, ","thi-ap7:5.2":"pabbajissasikincana; ","thi-ap7:5.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","thi-ap7:5.4":"nibbayissasinasava’. ","thi-ap7:6.1":"Idam vatvana sambuddho, ","thi-ap7:6.2":"tisso lokagganayako; ","thi-ap7:6.3":"Nabham abbhuggami viro, ","thi-ap7:6.4":"hamsarajava ambare. ","thi-ap7:7.1":"Sudinnam me danavaram, ","thi-ap7:7.2":"suyittha yagasampada; ","thi-ap7:7.3":"Katacchubhikkham datvana, ","thi-ap7:7.4":"pattaham acalam padam. ","thi-ap7:8.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","thi-ap7:8.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","thi-ap7:8.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","thi-ap7:8.4":"bhikkhadanassidam phalam. ","thi-ap7:9.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap7:9.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap7:9.3":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap7:10.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap7:10.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap7:10.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap7:11.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap7:11.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap7:11.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap7:12.1":"Ittham sudam katacchubhikkhadayika bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap7:13.1":"Katacchubhikkhadayikatheriyapadanam sattamam. "}